reviewText: Was ok nothing to really rave about.
It got it in a timely manner and am very happy with it....

I'm buying my Hallowe'en entertainment... I don't think I HAVE any
NATIONAL GEOGRAPHIC CHANNEL videos in my collection...
I bought this one:

FOOTNOTE:
IF you buy the other Nat'l Geo' Classics' title "MYSTERIES OF THE PARANORMAL"
You'll notice that four of these titles are---ALSO---on that collection:
1.) "Is It Real?: Ghosts"
2.) "Is It Real?: Vampires"
3.) "Is It Real?: Hauntings"
4.) "Taboo: Witchcraft"
BETWEEN THE TWO RELEASES, 8 of 11 titles are different [four are repeated{see above}].
So, if you have both sets, the DIFFERENT EPISODES are:
1.) "Is It Real?: Big Foot"-------- once.
2.) "Is It Real?: Big Foot"-------- once.
3.) "Taboo: Evil Spirits"---------- once.
